des:
This Skill is used by IT company for getting their project details and list of service in that respective projects. 
This help Client and customers to identify the services list and projects in there respective stream

Samples phrases are as follow::

Alexa open gtmservice

Alexa ask gtmservice for Count GTM Services
Alexa ask gtmservice for List GTM Services
Alexa ask gtmservice for How many GTM services we have
Alexa ask gtmservice for what is on GTM

Response would be a static depending on the phrases
